\c 12
\s Mirairo yekunatswa kwevakadzi
\p
\v 1 Zvino Jehovha wakataura kuna Mozisi achiti:
\v 2 Taura kuvana vaIsraeri uchiti: Kana mukadzi akabata mimba, ndokubereka munhurume, ipapo achava asina kuchena mazuva manomwe, semazuva ekuparadzaniswa ari kumwedzi achava asina kuchena\x + 15.19.\x*.
\v 3 Zvino nezuva rerusere nyama yeganda repamberi yake ichadzingiswa\x + Gen. 17.12; Ruk. 1.59; 2.21; Joh. 7.22,23.\x*.
\v 4 Achazogara mazuva makumi matatu nematatu muropa rekuchenurwa kwake, haangabati chinhu chitsvene, uye haangapindi panzvimbo tsvene, kusvika mazuva ekuchenurwa kwake azadziswa.
\v 5 Asi kana akabereka munhukadzi, zvino achava asina kuchena mavhiki maviri, sepakuparadzaniswa kwake, achazogara mazuva makumi matanhatu nematatu muropa rekuchenurwa kwake.
\v 6 Zvino kana mazuva ekuchenurwa kwake azadziswa\x + Ruk. 2.22.\x*, pamwanakomana kana pamwanasikana, achauya negwayana regore rimwe chive chipo chinopiswa, nemwana wehangaiwa, kana njiva, kuva chipo chezvivi, kumukova wetende rekusangana kumupristi.
\v 7 Iye achaipa pamberi paJehovha, ndokumuitira chiyananiso; zvino achanatswa pakuyerera kweropa rake\x + 20.18.\x*. Uyu murairo waiye anozobereka munhurume kana munhukadzi.
\v 8 Zvino kana ruoko rwake rwusingawani zvinokwana gwayana, zvino achatora njiva mbiri kana vana vaviri vehangaiwa\x + 1.14; 5.7. Ruk. 2.24.\x*; imwe ive chipo chinopiswa\x + 12.6.\x*, neimwe ive chipo chezvivi; uye mupristi achamuitira chiyananiso, uye achava wakachena\x + 4.26.\x*.